title: About
text:
This is Logan Griffiths blog that dives into the math behind the 2010 Chargers missing the playoffs despite having the No.1 Offense and Defense that season.

Logan Griffiths is a triple major at the University of Nebraska-Lincoln that is majoring in Sports Media and Communications, Advertising and Public Relations, and Journalism. He plans on utilizing this blog to further his data analyst career as he is an aspiring data sports journalist.
